OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'unfair'
OL,4,Capprenticeship funding model
OL,6,FAt present, A Levels and some
OL,7,Fvocational qualifications are
OL,8,Favailable to islanders for free, but
OL,9,Ffor some apprenticeship subjects a
OL,10,Ffull fee is charged.
OL,12,FAnnual Jersey Education Fees:
OL,14,FCurrently it is free to study A
OL,15,FLevels, BTECs or a vocational course
OL,16,Fat Highlands College or Hautlieu.
