OL,6,FFees for these courses are
OL,7,Fsignificantly higher, ranging between
OL,8,F#1,500 and #27,000 - and can take
OL,9,Fbetween 9 months and 5 years to
OL,10,Fcomplete.
OL,12,FThe review saw several other key
OL,13,Fthemes identified:
