OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'unfair'
OL,4,Capprenticeship funding model
OL,6,FRespondents also added: "The current
OL,7,Fgrant amount does not reflect the true
OL,8,Fcost of delivering high-quality
OL,9,Ftraining. In response, some local
OL,10,Ftraining providers reduce their fees
OL,11,Fto match the maximum grant available
OL,12,Fas closely as possible. However, this
OL,13,Fcan lead to compromises in the quality
OL,14,Fof training because providers have
OL,15,Ffewer resources to invest in delivery."
