OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'unfair'
OL,4,Capprenticeship funding model
OL,6,FIn response to the review, Jersey's
OL,7,FMinister for Education and Lifelong
OL,8,FLearning, Deputy Rob Ward said: "This
OL,9,Fengagement with stakeholders was
OL,10,Fdesigned to help us understand what
OL,11,Faspects of the current financial
OL,12,Fsupport system for apprenticeships
OL,13,Fwork well and where it can be improved.
OL,15,F"The ambition is to strike a fair
OL,16,Fbalance between competing needs and
OL,17,Fdemands. This includes calls from
OL,18,Findustry representatives for help with
OL,19,Fthe costs of training, which can vary
OL,20,Fsignificantly by sector.
